      "content": "OpenAPI surface for the Temple Health FHIR R4 endpoint, Temple University Health System's CMS Interoperability and Patient Access (CMS-9115-F) compliant HL7 FHIR Release 4.0.1 API powered by Epic's August 2025 release. Exposes USCDI-aligned clinical resources to third-party patient-access applications under SMART on FHIR / OAuth 2.0. Only a subset of the 80+ supported FHIR resource types is documented here — refer to the live CapabilityStatement for the full surface.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Epic on FHIR",
